<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Inline styles for email compatibility */
        .mail-body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #160F29;
            background-color: #F0F2EF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .mail-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }
        .mail-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #368F8B, #246A73);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .mail-header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 22px; }
        .mail-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .mail-section { padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .mail-info { background-color: #F0F2EF; border-left: 4px solid #368F8B; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 6px; }
        .mail-info-title { color: #246A73; font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 12px; }
        .mail-row { margin: 0 0 8px; }
        .mail-label { font-weight: 600; color: #160F29; display: inline-block; min-width: 120px; }
        .mail-value { color: #160F29; }
        .mail-message { border: 1px solid #368F8B; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 16px; }
        .mail-message-content { margin: 0; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; }
        .mail-actions { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; }
        .mail-button { display: inline-block; background: #F3DFC1; color: #160F29; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
        .mail-tip { margin-top: 24px; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; }
        .mail-footer { background-color: #160F29; color: #ffffff; padding: 16px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="mail-body">
    <div class="mail-container">
        <div class="mail-header">
            <div class="mail-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-paw"></i></div>
            <h1><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> Nouveau message depuis HowIMetMyHuman</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="mail-section">
            <p>Bonjour,</p>
            <p>Vous avez reçu un nouveau message via la plateforme <strong>HowIMetMyHuman</strong>.</p>

            <div class="mail-info">
                <h2 class="mail-info-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-clipboard-list"></i> Informations du contact</h2>
                <p class="mail-row"><span class="mail-label">Nom :</span><span class="mail-value">{{ data.name }}</span></p>
                <p class="mail-row"><span class="mail-label">Email :</span><span class="mail-value"><a href="mailto:{{ data.email }}">{{ data.email }}</a></span></p>
                {% if data.phone %}
                    <p class="mail-row"><span class="mail-label">Téléphone :</span><span class="mail-value">{{ data.phone }}</span></p>
                {% endif %}
                <p class="mail-row"><span class="mail-label">Sujet :</span><span class="mail-value">{{ data.subject }}</span></p>
            </div>

            <div class="mail-message">
                <h2 class="mail-info-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i> Message</h2>
                <p class="mail-message-content">{{ data.message|nl2br }}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mail-actions">
                <a href="mailto:{{ data.email }}?subject=Re: {{ data.subject|url_encode }}" class="mail-button">
                    Répondre à {{ data.name }}
                </a>
            </div>

            <p class="mail-tip">
                <strong>Conseil :</strong> Pensez à répondre dans les 48h pour offrir une meilleure expérience aux adoptants potentiels.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mail-footer">
            <p><strong>HowIMetMyHuman</strong> - Plateforme de mise en relation adoptants / associations</p>
            <p>Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre directement.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
